headline.main: Position of England in the War.

docs.lead_paragraph: The interest taken by our people in the last news from England is not a little remarkable. A break up in the Cabinet at Washington would scarcely occasion more remark or excitement than the withdrawal of Lord JOHN RUSSELL from the English Ministry. docs.lead_paragraph: The U.S. mail steamer Atlantic, from Liverpool about 2 o'clock afternoon of Saturday, the 27th January, arrived at her dock yesterday morning. The Atlantic arrived out at 5 o'clock, morning of Monday, the 22d. The steamship Great Britain arrived at Liverpool on 24th, with dates from Australia to Oct 26, and in specie [pound]350,000 sterling.

headline.main: A Know-Nothing Lady's Opinion on Politics.

docs.lead_paragraph: To the Editor of the New-York Daily Times: "'Tis a pity when charming women Talk of things which they don't understand. I Know the song very well. Lend me your pity then. Mr. J. H. WAINWRIGHT lately delivered an admirable address upon "Politics and Patriotism," giving us the true definition of the latter word, which I, like everybody else, (judging by the present state of things,) had entirely forgotten.
